__Benefits to Clients Using the Railway Tender Price Prediction Application__

**Profitability Improvement:**

Accurate price predictions enable clients to optimize bids, increasing profitability by 4-6%.

**Cost Optimization:**

Data-driven pricing reduces budgeting errors, cutting operational costs by 3-5%.

**Efficiency in Bidding:**

Streamlined bidding process saves time, improving efficiency by 30-40%.

**Competitive Edge:**

Insights into tender trends boost win rates by 8-10%.

**Risk Mitigation:**

Outlier detection reduces losses, cutting pricing errors by 5-7%.

**Enhanced Stakeholder Confidence:**

Data-backed decisions build trust, leading to better relationships and long-term growth.
